{"tid":815299,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"超強颱風山竹 新界人攻略","createTime":"2018-09-12T03:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T11:45:54.000Z","uid":122068,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"681111716dc88ab66c36f0f436c43d060b2c189f","tid":815299,"uid":122068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"呢個風球嘅路向或資料， 我相信唔少人都出post講過，喺度唔再重複。<br />\n所以想講下避難措施<br />\n<br />\n如果個風喺東面登陸， 雖然比起西登引起嘅影響可能少，但住喺新界嘅你哋都不容忽視<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/100432_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F100432_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff7f96d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/100447_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F100447_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d09ada78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/100455_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F100455_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7afd7995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 預防措施</span><br />\n1.喺個風嚟之前， 多d要留意下道路單車路坑渠，有冇樹葉垃圾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由於有啲路段比較偏僻未必有清潔姐姐會打掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果留意到有就麻煩致電1823， 喺呢幾日快快派人嚟清潔，如果唔係好容易會水浸！<br />\n<br />\n2. 當天唔好進行户外活動，打風仲行山玩溪降嘅人出咗事唔好打999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你要死唔好拉住人哋陪你一齊<br />\n<br />\n3.窗戶黐膠紙<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gsJEWGyi6yM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgsJEWGyi6yM&d=%2Fw%2Buz7xwB5ubYUDeAToF1JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=7645c8fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gsJEWGyi6yM</a><br />\n檢查露台或者屋企出面嘅嘢, 植物衣架要收返入屋， 冷氣機支架睇下穩唔穩陣<br />\n4. 準備電筒尿袋食糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新界圍村好容易停電， 試過有次紅雨就斷咗電<br />\n<br />\n5. 僭建物<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 東面登陸即係話新界好多地方會食硬啲風， 新界人要留喺安全地方。尤其是新界而家好多地方都有僭建物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多都係鐵皮搭成， 所以奉勸各位新界人小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/095333_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F095333_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=58c8a2db&s={SIZE}\" /> 隨便搵幅圖都可見九成九村屋都有僭建物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一旦個風冇減弱到... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢哋吹走嘅可能性......"},{"pid":"cfd1172f7d9149cd12cd4793992bb466ff4d6a75","tid":815299,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:08:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"028a08620042f4b11304570844d7a2546e38c1e9","tid":815299,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:10:00.000Z","msg":"手持午餐肉有西屌"},{"pid":"7f3d2f5e9aa2c95e76ef7e4b62c5050990d575fe","tid":815299,"uid":122068,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"5.舊式村屋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/111218_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F111218_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=83675baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實而家新界圍村仲有唔少舊式嘅村屋， 係傳統嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">木樑瓦頂</span>設計， 由於手藝失傳、缺乏維修保養等原因， 好多都有漏水、白蟻甚至間屋出現結構問題。 所以如果真係有啲唔對路， 煩請您執拾包袱， 馬上離開<br />\n<br />\n你可以選擇到你附近嘅<br />\n村公所（如有）<br />\n鄰居家裏（ 新式村屋）<br />\n臨 時 庇 護 中 心<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/public_services/emergency_services/emergency.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic_services%2Femergency_services%2Femergency.htm&d=%2Fw%2Buz7xwB5ubYUDeAToF1JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=996104c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/public_services/emergency_services/emergency.htm</a>"},{"pid":"968542591e3950d155e429e0cb4aaab2d17b30b5","tid":815299,"uid":150431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"支持樓主，正氣post"},{"pid":"eb4c4ef533a6234c4f15c38fe6f01e03cd083313","tid":815299,"uid":122068,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:25:58.000Z","msg":"6.水浸入屋<br />\n<br />\n以為住新式村屋或者住屋邨就冇事？<br />\n新界仍有唔少係靠海或者係處低窪地區， 因此低層人士會容易有水浸問題， 當水浸發生，你應該<br />\n6.1<span style=\"color: red;\"> 即刻閂總制 </span><br />\n6.2 留意水位上升速度， 如果上升太快就要即刻離開<br />\n6.3 如果水位上升速度緩慢， 就可以將電器置上較高位置<br />\n6.4 如果你嘅單位一向有水浸問題， 就要預先堆沙包木版， 並制定逃走路線<br />\n<br />\n假如真係要避難嘅話呀，你可以選擇攜帶"},{"pid":"a06780299f3fb4b21ccdc8b679480a4b97f0ed3b","tid":815299,"uid":46769,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"勸大家入定糧食 食水<br />\n手機/尿袋叉定電<br />\n小心家居啲玻璃<br />\n唔好睇少呢個風 細路仔可以Google下咩係溫黛 山竹可能同佢有得揮甚至勁過<br />\n唔好講咩有冇得放假/要有個風考驗下香港咁膚淺 真係有事你唔會咁講<br />\n如果最後個風打唔中/黎到香港冇料到 我最多比大家笑下 但食正個風真係會死人/財產損失<br />\n希望大家認真對待今次颱風"},{"pid":"75cbccc67807500a5326dcd23acc33c0b137e343","tid":815299,"uid":122068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eb4c4ef533a6234c4f15c38fe6f01e03cd083313","tid":815299,"uid":122068,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:25:58.000Z","msg":"6.水浸入屋<br />\n<br />\n以為住新式村屋或者住屋邨就冇事？<br />\n新界仍有唔少係靠海或者係處低窪地區， 因此低層人士會容易有水浸問題， 當水浸發生，你應該<br />\n6.1<span style=\"color: red;\"> 即刻閂總制 </span><br />\n6.2 留意水位上升速度， 如果上升太快就要即刻離開<br />\n6.3 如果水位上升速度緩慢， 就可以將電器置上較高位置<br />\n6.4 如果你嘅單位一向有水浸問題， 就要預先堆沙包木版， 並制定逃走路線<br />\n<br />\n假如真係要避難嘅話呀，你可以選擇攜帶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/112645_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F112645_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a1be119a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"270159425b5af5c5c25f379d2a1abea52205e397","tid":815299,"uid":122068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:38:05.000Z","msg":"7. 家中寵物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7.1如果安全唔洗走嘅話<a href=\"http://blog.pettalk.tw/2015/08/17/別讓颱風嚇壞毛寶貝！颱風又來了貓狗怎麼辦？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.pettalk.tw%2F2015%2F08%2F17%2F%E5%88%A5%E8%AE%93%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E5%9A%87%E5%A3%9E%E6%AF%9B%E5%AF%B6%E8%B2%9D%EF%BC%81%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E5%8F%88%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86%E8%B2%93%E7%8B%97%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E8%BE%A6%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=%2Fw%2Buz7xwB5ubYUDeAToF1JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=2a200c53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blog.pettalk.tw/2015/08/17/別讓颱風嚇壞毛寶貝！颱風又來了貓狗怎麼辦？/</a><br />\n<br />\n7.2如果居住地方唔安全，真係要走<br />\n遇上災害 怎麼保護家中寵物 <a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/8/29/n8247258.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F16%2F8%2F29%2Fn8247258.htm&d=%2Fw%2Buz7xwB5ubYUDeAToF1JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=77b61d25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/8/29/n8247258.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8c974fdc862d53a25a5f669ce2aa02ea8fa773c8","tid":815299,"uid":122068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T22:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/062740_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F062740_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=85e5c270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1315740/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1315740%2F&d=%2Fw%2Buz7xwB5ubYUDeAToF1JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=f8f10335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1315740/</a><br />\n有鑑於呢個風已經升為五級颶風， 香港人可以選擇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返內地渡假or 飛到其他地方暫避<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當天唔好再追風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 離開海岸海旁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以及到高地， 因為吹襲嘅時候 遇上風暴潮有機會引起超過五米高嘅巨浪<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/064344_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F064344_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a897c097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/064443_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F064443_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5368ff93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/064723_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F064723_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ea2bf278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/064836_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F064836_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=eebfd38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/065158_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F065158_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=966543e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料來源<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2veJYPcfTbw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2veJYPcfTbw&d=%2Fw%2Buz7xwB5ubYUDeAToF1JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=5db44b00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2veJYPcfTbw</a><br />\n<br />\n9 水浸黑點<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dsd.gov.hk/TC/Flood_Prevention/Our_Flooding_Situation/Flooding_Blackspots/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dsd.gov.hk%2FTC%2FFlood_Prevention%2FOur_Flooding_Situation%2FFlooding_Blackspots%2Findex.html&d=%2Fw%2Buz7xwB5ubYUDeAToF1JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=98d276d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dsd.gov.hk/TC/Flood_Prevention/Our_Flooding_Situation/Flooding_Blackspots/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"2c59ce2c50ebb66c1726fa75b92b35d71b2f6b89","tid":815299,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T22:56:06.000Z","msg":"高質"},{"pid":"1e4310a051df92b8cc4aea5fb89e58ec148e35ba","tid":815299,"uid":97551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T00:51:58.000Z","msg":"回內地暫避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n我本身今日飛內地 星期日返黎<br />\n如果真係飛左 我最快都要星期三先有飛機返黎<br />\n<br />\n我最後都係驚要返工所以取消左<br />\n你睇下我幾撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ebfa53948e246431f90971b65ebaf183983050","tid":815299,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T00:55:07.000Z","msg":"等睇星期日出太陽"},{"pid":"605ad1ff03f0b4c9ed816ddcdd38593d2417c44a","tid":815299,"uid":72676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:02:03.000Z","msg":"E家唔係吹唔成咩"},{"pid":"dca34e99d84d505345e47fd5dc2db08263b978fd","tid":815299,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:09:25.000Z","msg":"天地有正氣"},{"pid":"b9136d599e41f634e6a4c6dfa075506f1ad66f0c","tid":815299,"uid":16880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e4310a051df92b8cc4aea5fb89e58ec148e35ba","tid":815299,"uid":97551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T00:51:58.000Z","msg":"回內地暫避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n我本身今日飛內地 星期日返黎<br />\n如果真係飛左 我最快都要星期三先有飛機返黎<br />\n<br />\n我最後都係驚要返工所以取消左<br />\n你睇下我幾撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:27:26.000Z","msg":"搭高鐵翻黎咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a167521b162e8a8ef9b5672a8ae8b65d196bef","tid":815299,"uid":122068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:45:54.000Z","msg":"10. 高樓大廈安全 <br />\n<br />\n10.1高廈搖擺<br />\n<br />\n香港新聞網7月25日電  強颱風韋森特襲港期間，全港多區大廈的住戶均報稱感到搖晃，<span style=\"color: red;\">搖到頭暈</span>；部分住所內外&ldquo;傷痕纍纍&rdquo;，包括外牆批盪剝落、窗戶損毀，專家指大廈在強風下搖晃屬正常現象，足以抵受10號風球或以上風力，<span style=\"color: red;\">以樓高約30層的大廈為例，擺動範圍約200毫米(20厘米) </span>。<br />\n<br />\n現代樓宇入圖則前，均要先評估樓宇有可能面對的陣風和平均風力，以評估安全擺動幅度，足以抵禦10號風球，而以樓高約30層的大廈為例，擺動範圍約200毫米，即使風力超逾10號風球，大廈物料仍有安全系數，不會倒塌；而1950年代前落成的大廈，雖然入則時毋須計算風力，但由於樓層矮，承受的風力相對小，故亦不會有被強風吹倒的風險。<br />\n<br />\n10.2電梯門開關失靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，多處電梯亦出現電梯門未能關上的狀況，致電梯無法正常運作，理工大學機械工程學系工程師盧覺強解釋，<span style=\"color: red;\">由於有氣流吹入升降機槽，而強風同一時間由大堂吹至，兩股氣流造成電梯門內外壓力不一，結果不能順利開關</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2012/0725/151034.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2012%2F0725%2F151034.shtml&d=%2Fw%2Buz7xwB5ubYUDeAToF1JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=730c2323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2012/0725/151034.shtml</a>"}]}